{"type": "article", "id": 12389, "title": "“无限 C”灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135745IPXuNfeo7HB9ESLO.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款台灯叫做 “无限 C”，来自韩国设计师 Jung Dongsung，这个充满未来感的灯具可以被“拗”成“0”或 “9” 等酷酷的造型，顶部的环形框架里面设置了一个 LED 灯，圆形的顶部可以化身触摸屏，展示天气，窗口小工具，或是和智能手机配合使用。颜色上，台灯有五种色系选择，而且对比色的使用凸显着设计细节上的用心。<a href=\"http://www.jungdongsung.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>进入设计师个人主页，可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401497jMiefmpZQgwnLSd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401491icxemsD8dbSBwkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140150W56hDbTNxYlU7fZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48655257\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140150j5CQnda9VFHhIitG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40586797\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140151VrO7DoB1TQFwKzUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140151nUvhtYskQ2RMHaE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}